{"word":"ἀξίως","slug":"ἀξίως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀξίως</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄξιος\">ἄξιος</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> ‘in a manner that does honor to’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> of the entity honored by the behavior cited in the context <b><i>worthily</i> <a href='B:520 16:2'>Ro 16:2</a>; <a href='B:560 4:1'>Eph 4:1</a>; <a href='B:570 1:27'>Phil 1:27</a>; <a href='B:590 2:12'>1 Th 2:12</a>; <a href='B:710 1:1'>3 J 6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀξιόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀόρατος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}